text: aur hamane isaraeeliyon ko samudr paar kara diya. phir firaun aur usakee senaon ne sarakashee aur zyaadatee ke saath unaka peechha kiya, yahaan tak ki jab vah doobane laga to pukaar utha, "main eemaan le aaya ki usake siv koee poojy-prabhu nahee, jis par isaraeel kee santaan eemaan laee. ab main aagyaakaaree hoon.
